room_title: Escape room "Incantation" by Time to Escape in Okeechobee
room_description:
The High Wizard Bairamint has been captured and the lands are in peril. There is only one thing that can save us all and that is the Wand of Shadows. It is up to you to find the Wand of Shadows and free the High Wizard before it is too late.
But first, you must overcome the obstacles left to prevent that from happening. The Wizard's lair is heavily protected and you must first gain entry and then solve the clues that have been left by Bairamint in order to find the Wand.
